{"TopicId":136050,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"[OUTDATED] Simplified/Shortened forum rules","CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-04T18:29:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-04T18:29:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EThis is an unofficial easier-to-read and short version of the forum rules for those who find the official version difficult to understand. The official guidelines can be found \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/guidelines/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehere\u003C/a\u003E. The official version contains a lot of clarifications and explanations, so please look there before questioning anything, and please let me know if I can improve this summary in any way.\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#A52A2A;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E1. In general\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003E(1.2-1.5 \u0026amp; 5.2)\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E \u003C/strong\u003EHopefully, these rules will help us all\u003Cstrong\u003E \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#A52A2A;\u0022\u003Erespect each other\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E. If you don\u0027t obey the rules, you might get punished for it. If you try to get around a punishment, you will get permanently banned.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E2. Messages and other text/links\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003E(2.1-2.2)\u003C/span\u003E No \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Esoftware piracy, politics, religion, adult stuff, racism\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E or \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Esexism\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E. Don\u0027t be \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Erude\u003C/strong\u003E \u003C/span\u003Eto anyone, and keep private messages private. No \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eswearing\u003C/strong\u003E \u003C/span\u003Eor trying to get around the language filter. \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDon\u0027t accuse\u003C/strong\u003E \u003C/span\u003Esomeone of anything unless you can prove it. Don\u0027t use links that earn someone money, like\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003E \u003Cstrong\u003Ead.fly\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E, and no\u003Cstrong\u003E \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003Eroleplay \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E(\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/132441-whats-the-story-behind-the-roleplay-guideline/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#008080;\u0022\u003Ehere\u0027s the reason for that rule\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003E(2.3-2.4)\u003C/span\u003E Make your posts meaningful: \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eno \u201Cbump\u201D or \u201Clike\u201D\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E messages or just sending\u003Cstrong\u003E \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003Ereaction images\u003C/span\u003E. \u003C/strong\u003EDon\u0027t deliberately \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eannoy anyone\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E or take the thread \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eoff topic\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E, and never ask when the\u003Cstrong\u003E \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003Enext version of KSP\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E is going to be released (\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Ealso applies to mods\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E if someone has already asked). New threads should be started in the correct part of the forum, and all posts should be in plain \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FF8C00;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EEnglish \u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E(unless it\u0027s in the \u201CInternational\u201D section).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#008000;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E2.5 Old threads\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\nYou are allowed to post something \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#008000;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Emeaningful\u003C/strong\u003E \u003C/span\u003Ein old threads, but remember that a lot of people don\u0027t like it. If someone else posts in an old thread,\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#008000;\u0022\u003E \u003Cstrong\u003Edon\u0027t complain\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#0000CD;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E3 Moderators etc.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003E(3.1-3.5)\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E \u003C/strong\u003EIf you see anything wrong, press the\u003Cstrong\u003E \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#0000FF;\u0022\u003E\u201CReport post\u201D\u003C/span\u003E \u003C/strong\u003Ebutton at the top of the post instead of talking about it in the thread. \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#0000CD;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENever pretend to be a moderator\u003C/strong\u003E \u003C/span\u003Eor to work for Squad, contact them outside the community in their private time or openly talk about their decisions to ban or punish etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#800080;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E4 Your account and personal information\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:100%;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003E(4.1-4.4)\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#800080;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E Keep your account and personal information safe\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E. You are only allowed to have \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#800080;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eone account\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E and you must\u003Cstrong\u003E \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#800080;\u0022\u003Enot share it with anyone\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E. If you\u0027re younger than 18, don\u0027t post pictures of your face and don\u0027t tell anyone how old you are.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-04T21:07:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTL;DR. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKidding aside, while I appreciate what you\u0027re trying to do, having two versions of the rules is likely a bad idea. The moderators deal with enough \u0022rules-lawyers\u0022 who try to end around the spirit of the rules by taking as literal an interpretation as possible (while conveniently ignoring the \u0022Take Note\u0022 section), having another official version of the rules would only add ammunition for them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-07T22:21:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222494678\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136050\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221459804044\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 04/04/2016 at 11:07 PM, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe moderators deal with enough \u0022rules-lawyers\u0022 who try to end around the spirit of the rules by taking as literal an interpretation as possible (while conveniently ignoring the \u0022Take Note\u0022 section), having another official version of the rules would only add ammunition for them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry to hear that, Red. I actually didn\u0027t intend this to be an official version so much as an aid to\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eunderstanding\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0the official version. But I can see where even that could cause problems. Shall I delete the OP?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-07T22:24:23Z\u0022 title=\u002204/07/2016 10:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 7, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Deddly\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-07T22:27:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222494361\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136050\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221459794568\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/4/2016 at 8:29 PM, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ndon\u0027t post pictures of your face\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCase in point, this could be taken two ways...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-07T23:20:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222501023\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136050\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460067677\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n59 minutes ago, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry to hear that, Red. I actually didn\u0027t intend this to be an official version so much as an aid to\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eunderstanding\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0the official version. But I can see where even that could cause problems. Shall I delete the OP?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs long as it\u0027s not represented as an official version I think it\u0027s fine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-08T01:27:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSounds like a pretty good idea to me!\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nI have a couple of suggestions:\u003Cbr\u003E\nAdd a bolded link to the forum rules, with instructions saying to check there if you want clarification on rules.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nI don\u0027t want to be nitpicky, but I think you might want to change this typo:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222494361\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136050\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221459794568\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/4/2016 at 11:29 AM, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntake the threat \u003Cstrong\u003Eoff topic\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd you might want to clarify that this to be about staff/moderation decisions, rather than the general nature of those actions:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222494361\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136050\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221459794568\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/4/2016 at 11:29 AM, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nabout bans or punishments etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFinally, since this was posted, a new rule was added, 2.3f:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/136207-new-rule-repeated-requests-for-add-on-updates-are-now-forbidden/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAgain, just because I have some criticism, I don\u0027t think this is a bad idea. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-08T06:59:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell I did ask for feedback, so I really apppreciate it! Will implement your suggestions later.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-17T20:52:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI finally got around to updating this according to your suggestions, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/139256-mad-rocket-scientist/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022139256\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/139256-mad-rocket-scientist/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Mad Rocket Scientist\u003C/a\u003E. Thanks for your help.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI also added a link to the conversation about the \u0022no roleplay\u0022 rule. If anyone knows any other threads I could link to explaining other rules, I\u0027m happy to add more links.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222501041\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136050\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460068060\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152460\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022swjr-swis\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2016-04-07 at 0:27 AM, swjr-swis said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCase in point, this could be taken two ways...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow so? Any suggestion on how I could make it clearer?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-17T20:53:23Z\u0022 title=\u002204/17/2016 08:53  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 17, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Deddly\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-17T21:12:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222519072\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136050\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460926323\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 minutes ago, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\